oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Effects of pre-sprouting and nitrogen fertilization on the yield of table potatoes
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Mustonen, Leo
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: Crop husbandry
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: The effects of pre-sprouting and nitrogen fertilization on the yield of common table potatoes were studied at MTT Agrifood Research Finland during 1993-1994.
oai_dc:dc.dc:identifier: Mustonen, Leo (2006) Effects of pre-sprouting and nitrogen fertilization on the yield of table potatoes. In: NJF Report, Nordic Association of Agricultural Scientists, 2 (1), NJF Report, p. 46.
